Privacy Policy
Your privacy is important to us. It is LUXSANK/LUXSAM's policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect from you across our website, apps, themes, and watch faces, and other sites we own and operate.
Information We Collect
We may collect personal and non-personal information from you for the purposes described below:
Location Data
:
Some of our apps and watch faces may collect location data to provide functionality, such as weather updates, personalized services, or location-based features. This data is collected only with your explicit consent and is processed securely.
We do not share your location data with third parties, except as required by law or as necessary to provide the requested functionality (e.g., integration with weather services).
Advertising Data (AdMob)
:
Certain apps may display ads using Google AdMob. AdMob may collect and use data, such as device information and user interactions with ads, to deliver personalized or non-personalized ads.
For more information on how Google AdMob collects and uses data, please refer to
Google's AdMob Privacy Policy
.
Other Data
:
We may collect data, such as email addresses or other personal information, if provided by you for customer support or account-related purposes. This data is collected and stored securely.
How We Use the Information
We only collect and use your data for the following purposes:
To provide and improve the functionality of our apps, themes, and watch faces.
To deliver personalized or non-personalized ads (where applicable).
To enable features that require location services (e.g., weather updates).
To comply with legal obligations or respond to lawful requests.
Data Sharing
We do not share any personally identifiable information with third parties, except in the following cases:
To provide features or services you request (e.g., weather data).
When required by law, such as in response to a subpoena or other legal process.
Third-Party Services
Our apps may use third-party services, such as Google AdMob, to provide ads or analytics. These services may collect and process data in accordance with their respective privacy policies. We recommend reviewing the privacy policies of these third-party services for more information:
Google AdMob Privacy Policy
Your Choices
You can choose to:
Disable location permissions for our apps in your device settings. Note that certain features may not work as intended without access to location data.
Opt out of personalized ads through the Google Ads settings on your device.
Data Retention
We only retain collected information for as long as necessary to provide you with the requested service or as required by law. All data is securely processed and stored using commercially acceptable measures to prevent loss, theft, and unauthorized access.
Changes to This Policy
This policy may be updated from time to time. We encourage you to review it periodically. This policy is effective as of December 2021 and was last updated in December 2024.
If you have any questions about this policy or your data, please contact us at luxsank.luxsam@gmail.com.
